high_descs: Go to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the lettuce on top of the knife.
Turn around and take the lettuce to the fridge.
Put the lettuce leaf in the fridge to cool it off.
Take the cold lettuce to the trash can by the toaster.
Put the cold lettuce in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a cold lettuce leaf.

high_descs: Turn around to go to the counter behind you, with the stove on your right.
Pick up the head of lettuce that is closer to the front of the counter.
Turn around and cross the room to the refrigerator.
Put the lettuce on the top shelf of the refrigerator, behind the egg, closing the door, then take the lettuce out again and re-close the door.
Turn to face the opposite direction and go to the red wastebasket.
Throw the lettuce into the wastebasket.
anns.task_desc: Throw a chilled head of lettuce away into a red wastebasket.

high_descs: Turn left, move forward, then turn left to face the counter with the lettuce.
Pick up the lettuce nearest to you from the counter.
Go to the fridge behind you.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge.
Turn right, go forward, then turn right to go to the trash can.
Put the lettuce in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put cold lettuce in the trash.
